column16: George Kottaras strikes out on foul tip.
Prince Fielder doubles (10) on a line drive to center fielder Ryan Spilborghs.    Corey Hart scores.
Tony Abreu grounds into a force out, fielded by second baseman Eric Young.    Justin Upton out at 2nd.
Justin Upton singles on a line drive to center fielder Dexter Fowler.    Cole Gillespie scores.    Stephen Drew to 3rd.
Augie Ojeda grounds out, second baseman Eric Young to first baseman Jason Giambi.    Cole Gillespie to 2nd.
Cole Gillespie singles on a ground ball to second baseman Eric Young, deflected by pitcher Juan Rincon.
Chris Snyder flies out to left fielder Seth Smith.
